Source: halos-halpi-desktop-branding
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Matti Airas <matti.airas@hatlabs.fi>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/hatlabs/halos-halpi-desktop-branding
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: halos-halpi-desktop-branding
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         rpd-common
Provides: halos-desktop-wallpaper
Conflicts: halos-desktop-wallpaper
Replaces: halos-desktop-wallpaper,
          rpd-common
Description: HALPI2 branded default desktop wallpaper
 This package provides the HALPI2-branded default desktop wallpaper for
 HaLOS HALPI2 desktop variants. It ships pcmanfm system-wide
 desktop-items conffiles that override the upstream Raspberry Pi OS
 defaults at /etc/xdg/pcmanfm/default/. Per-user wallpaper choices in
 ~/.config/pcmanfm/ take precedence over this default.
 .
 File ownership at the canonical paths is taken from rpd-common via
 Replaces:; rpd-common stays installed and its other files are
 unaffected. Exclusivity with the generic HaLOS branding
 (halos-desktop-branding) is enforced via the virtual package
 halos-desktop-wallpaper: only one provider can be installed at a
 time. Pi-gen pre-installs this package on HALPI2 desktop builds so
 the HALPI2-specific artwork wins over the generic default.
